      | <>                      |

  @positive
  @deprecated
  Scenario Outline: Change Dropdown input width to <width>
    When I set inputWidth to "<width>"
    Then inputWidth is set to "<width>"
    Examples:
      | width |
      | 1     |
      | 10    |
      | 100   |

  @negative
  @deprecated
  Scenario Outline: Set out of scope characters to Dropdown input width to <width>
